bile</li>\n<li>⛔️ Unsubscription support with cookies</li>\n<li>🎉 Built with TypeScript</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>\n  <a name=\"installation\" href=\"#installation\">\n  </a>\n  Installation\n</h2>\n\n<h4>\n  <a name=\"yarn\" href=\"#yarn\">\n  </a>\n  yarn\n</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight shell\"><code>yarn add use-exit-intent\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h4>\n  <a name=\"npm\" href=\"#npm\">\n  </a>\n  npm\n</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight shell\"><code>npm i use-exit-intent\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2>\n  <a name=\"importing\" href=\"#importing\">\n  </a>\n  Importing\n</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight tsx\"><code><span class=\"k\">import</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"nx\">useExitIntent</span> <span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"k\">from</span> <span class=\"dl\">'</span><span class=\"s1\">use-exit-intent</span><span class=\"dl\">'</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2>\n  <a name=\"using\" href=\"#using\">\n  </a>\n  Using\n</h2>\n\n<p>In your React component:</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"highlight js-code-highlight\">\n<pre class=\"highlight tsx\"><code><span class=\"k\">export</span> <span class=\"kd\">function</span> <span class=\"nx\">App</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"kd\">const</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"nx\">registerHandler</span> <span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nx\">useExitIntent</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n\n  <span class=\"nx\">registerHandler</span><span class=\"p\">({</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">id</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"dl\">'</span><span class=\"s1\">openModal</span><span class=\"dl\">'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">handler</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"nx\">console</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">log</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"dl\">'</span><span class=\"s1\">Hello from handler!</span><span class=\"dl\">'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">})</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c1\">// ...</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight__panel js-actions-panel\">\n<div class=\"highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on\"><title>Enter fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-off\"><title>Exit fullscreen mode</title>\n    <path d=\"M18 7h4v2h-6V3h2v4zM8 9H2V7h4V3h2v6zm10 8v4h-2v-6h6v2h-4zM8 15v6H6v-4H2v-2h6z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>To get more knowledge about this hook</strong>:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://daltonmenezes.github.io/use-exit-intent/docs/getting-started/overview\">Docs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://daltonmenezes.github.io/use-exit-intent/#playground\">Playground</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/daltonmenezes/use-exit-intent\">GitHub Repository</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n","body_markdown":"The Exit Intent strategy is a great way to increase your conversion rate. That strategy is commonly used to show a modal/popup when the user is about to leave your website.\n\n[useExitIntent](https://daltonmenezes.github.io/use-exit-intent) hook is simple to use and you can customize it to your needs. Here are the main features:\n\n- 🚀 Multiple handlers can be registred\n- 🔥 Highly configurable\n- 🧠 Different strategies for Desktop and Mobile\n- ⛔️ Unsubscription support with cookies\n- 🎉 Built with TypeScript\n\n## Installation\n\n#### yarn\n\n```bash\nyarn add use-exit-intent\n```\n\n#### npm\n```bash\nnpm i use-exit-intent\n```\n\n<br/><br/>\n\n## Importing\n```tsx\nimport { useExitIntent } from 'use-exit-intent'\n```\n\n## Using\n\nIn your React component:\n\n<br />\n\n```tsx\nexport function App() {\n  const { registerHandler } = useExitIntent()\n\n  registerHandler({\n    id: 'openModal',\n    handler: () => console.log('Hello from handler!')\n  })\n\n  // ...\n}\n```\n**To get more knowledge about this hook**:\n- [Docs](https://daltonmenezes.github.io/use-exit-intent/docs/getting-started/overview)\n- [Playground](https://daltonmenezes.github.io/use-exit-intent/#playground)\n- [GitHub Repository](https://github.com/daltonmenezes/use-exit-intent)","user":{"name":"Dalton Menezes","username":"daltonmenezes","twitter_username":"daltonmenezes","github_username":"daltonmenezes","user_id":721838,"website_url":"https://daltonmenezes.github.io","profile_image":"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--n-o_Itot--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_640,q_auto,w_640/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/721838/a9e2e504-084a-4352-ab6c-1a9b9d392a31.png","profile_image_90":"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--URTR_ria--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_90,q_auto,w_90/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/721838/a9e2e504-084a-4352-ab6c-1a9b9d392a31.png"}}